Package: EffectVisR
Title: Customisable effect size plots with confidence intervals for scientific presentations and publications
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Fabian", family = "Schwendinger", email = "schwendinger.fabian@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person(given = "Eric", family = "Lichtenstein", email = "e.lichtenstein@unibas.ch", role = "aut")
    )
Description: This package provides functions to create customized effect size plots, visualising confidence intervals with a speedometer-like design. It simplifies the interpretation of effect sizes in relation to their confidence intervals.
License: CC BY-NC 4.0
Encoding: UTF-8
